Class MyWorld

  • java.lang.Object
    • greenfoot.World
      • MyWorld

  • public class MyWorld
extends greenfoot.World
    The MyWorld class is the foundation of the entire game, holding important variables that provide all other classes the information needed to perform their tasks. This includes player and enemy locations and spawning, and terrain generation, as well as the grid that the game revolves around This class also handles the switching of floors based on player location, and creating the gameover and gamewon screens
    Version:
    January 2019
    Author:
    Alexander, Daniel, Deston, Justin, Leo
